[30;1m248 | [0m[35m### Wait[0m
[30;1m249 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m250 | [0m[35mA `Wait` state waits for a given number of seconds, or until the current time[0m
[30;1m251 | [0m[35mhits a particular time. The time to wait may be taken from the execution's JSON[0m
[30;1m252 | [0m[35mstate.[0m
